<text id="02-output-contract" title="Stratified sampling recipe — output contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for sampling-recipe.json plus a valid and invalid worked example.</summary>

  <section title="JSON Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/eval-sampling-recipe",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["version", "parent_version", "created_at", "N_daily", "seed", "tail_floor", "head_cap_share", "strata", "drift_policy"],
  "properties": {
    "version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"},
    "parent_version": {"type": ["string", "null"]},
    "created_at": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time"},
    "N_daily": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 10, "maximum": 5000},
    "seed": {"type": "integer"},
    "tail_floor": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 50, "default": 5},
    "head_cap_share": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.1, "maximum": 0.6, "default": 0.4},
    "drift_policy": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["abs_share_threshold", "max_age_days"],
      "properties": {
        "abs_share_threshold": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.01, "maximum": 0.5},
        "max_age_days": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 90}
      }
    },
    "strata": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 2,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["key", "traffic_share", "quota"],
        "properties": {
          "key": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-z0-9._-]+$"},
          "traffic_share": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
          "quota": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1}
        }
      }
    }
  }
}]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "version": "1.2.0",
  "parent_version": "1.1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-05-22T07:00:00Z",
  "N_daily": 200,
  "seed": 42,
  "tail_floor": 5,
  "head_cap_share": 0.4,
  "drift_policy": {"abs_share_threshold": 0.1, "max_age_days": 30},
  "strata": [
    {"key": "cohort=enterprise.tool=search.intent=lookup", "traffic_share": 0.55, "quota": 80},
    {"key": "cohort=enterprise.tool=summarise.intent=long-form", "traffic_share": 0.20, "quota": 50},
    {"key": "cohort=smb.tool=search.intent=lookup", "traffic_share": 0.15, "quota": 35},
    {"key": "cohort=trial.tool=search.intent=lookup", "traffic_share": 0.10, "quota": 35}
  ]
}]]></code>
      <note>N_daily honoured (80+50+35+35=200), head capped at 40%, tail floor 5 respected (smallest quota 35 &gt; 5), seed locked.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "parent_version": null,
  "created_at": "2026-05-22T07:00:00Z",
  "N_daily": 200,
  "seed": 42,
  "tail_floor": 5,
  "head_cap_share": 0.4,
  "drift_policy": {"abs_share_threshold": 0.1, "max_age_days": 30},
  "strata": [
    {"key": "head", "traffic_share": 0.92, "quota": 184},
    {"key": "tail-a", "traffic_share": 0.05, "quota": 0},
    {"key": "tail-b", "traffic_share": 0.03, "quota": 16}
  ]
}]]></code>
      <note>Three violations: head quota 184/200 = 92% &gt; 40% cap (r3); tail-a quota 0 violates floor 5 (r1); sum 200 OK but quota distribution breaks rules.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>sum(quota) == N_daily.</item>
      <item>min(quota) ≥ tail_floor for every non-empty stratum.</item>
      <item>max(quota / N_daily) ≤ head_cap_share.</item>
      <item>seed is an integer, not a string or null.</item>
      <item>version, parent_version, created_at present and well-formed.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
